From Gordon Banks Subject Re Eugenics Probably within years a new type of eugenics will be Maybe even We are now mapping the human We will then start to work on manipulation of that Using genetic engineering we will be able to insert whatever genes we No breeding no hybrids The ethical question is should we do this Should we make a race of disease free long lived Arnold Schwartzenegger muscled supermen Even if we Gordon Banks Skepticism is the chastity of the intellect and it is shameful to surrender it too